<p><span style="text-decoration: underline;"><strong>Another Soul Joins The Halkost</strong></span><br />
<strong>Authors:</strong> <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/themightymcb" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(4483018); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=4483018&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1609721468" alt="TheMightyMcB" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=4483018)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/themightymcb" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(4483018); return false;">TheMightyMcB</a></span> and <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/n-aepic-fael" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(4463776); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=4463776&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1609721468" alt="N_Aepic_Fael" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=4463776)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/n-aepic-fael" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(4463776); return false;">N_Aepic_Fael</a></span><br />
